  Update dependencies per the consensus formed with ssuominen.

  10 Mar 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> mate-desktop-1.6.2.ebuild:
  Remove invalid SLOT dependencies from pkg-config, gettext and intltool.

  10 Mar 2014; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> mate-desktop-1.6.2.ebuild:
  Further review of dependencies.

*mate-desktop-1.6.2 (02 Mar 2014)

